{"tid":628543,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"Text message VS 直接打電話","createTime":"2018-04-14T03:37:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T03:58:20.000Z","uid":171720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9915950da172ce135e5c3767ba0a411303da0ab9","tid":628543,"uid":171720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:37:51.000Z","msg":"有時有緊要事<br />\n直接打電話比朋友 係長響無人接<br />\n但反而text message 佢就可以當下果刻覆<br />\n問佢係咪有野忙緊 其實就hea緊 <br />\n但就係唔中意聽電話咁<br />\n以前未有應用程式普及 大多數人都會直接打電話<br />\n而家想搵番之前同朋友煲電話粥果種感覺已經好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSor 1999"},{"pid":"6cab52848e6c05a8f8d3b49e8688958d448a8326","tid":628543,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"我會打電話<br />\n打字好煩"},{"pid":"0cebe06e938cb161edace53a2464e30711210dab","tid":628543,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:46:51.000Z","msg":"唔方便傾咪唔聽"},{"pid":"f544df143010190e83c96b2837fcdc3b61debd11","tid":628543,"uid":171720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cab52848e6c05a8f8d3b49e8688958d448a8326","tid":628543,"uid":36435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:44:22.000Z","msg":"我會打電話<br />\n打字好煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}